Package: hyperon-metta
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3
Recommends: cogutil, atomspace
Description: MeTTa programming language implementation for AGI
 Hyperon is a substantially revised, novel version of OpenCog that
 implements the MeTTa (Meta Type Talk) programming language. MeTTa
 provides type-theoretic foundations, meta-programming capabilities,
 and integration with the Distributed AtomSpace (DAS).
 .
 This package provides:
  - MeTTa language interpreter (Rust-based)
  - Python bindings for MeTTa
  - C API for integration with other components
  - REPL for interactive MeTTa programming

Package: hyperon-metta-dev
Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Depends: hyperon-metta (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: MeTTa programming language - development files
 This package contains the header files and development libraries
 needed to build applications that use the Hyperon MeTTa API.
